snippet.title: Gourdlets Narrated Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
🌈 Play the demo & wishlist on steam: http://s.team/a/2013730
💬 discord! https://discord.gg/xYgv78Azwe
💌 fan mailing list! https://forms.gle/HyTQ2ArH6CYgasqv6
📬streamer mailing list! https://tinyurl.com/2vbyzty4

Gourdlets is a city-building sandbox. Place buildings and scenery, and then watch visiting gourdlets arrive and interact with the world. No objectives, no points, just building.
